ss=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把死共狗為錢可以做呢d事，反正上庭d錢都係鄰國課金 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0e5e3035613ffaac547849eb036b9027e1906c","tid":326375,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:20:52.000Z","msg":"過咗海就係神仙"},{"pid":"c9716ca7f03c286167e6be51e5df1c922f40d5ad","tid":326375,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:32:22.000Z","msg":"【DQ四議員】非建制派補選至少失2席 失分組點票否決權<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170714/large/1500036785_71a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170714%2Flarge%2F1500036785_71a6.png&h=77328a36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼青年新政梁頌恆及游蕙禎被政府褫奪立法會議員資格後，法庭再裁定政府司法覆核勝訴，認為羅冠聰、劉小麗、梁國雄及姚松炎的宣誓不合規格，宣佈由去年10月12日宣誓當日起計，4人議席失效，若上訴失敗，便有6席要補選。科大社會學部副教授成名預計，建制派在九西及新東應最少奪2席，地區直選議席將增至18席，相反非建制派會減至17席，喪失在分組點票時的否決權。<br />\n<br />\n他分析，在九西及新東的兩大選區，建制派必然會派人參選，即使泛民派代表出戰補選，在比例代表制下，估計建制派會在九西及新東取得最少2席。而只有1席出缺的港島區，將按單議席單票制補選，估計對非建制派有利。<br />\n<br />\n至於非建制派能否有策略可全奪回6席，他稱，「我覺得係悲觀」，因在比例代表制下，建制派有一定核心的支持者，即鐵票，認為非建制派「無可能6席贏返晒返來」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56957050&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170714\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56957050%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170714&d=nQDymLHpC61b3hBQzZxSKZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=ad9ff36a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56957050%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170714&h=5dd843a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56957050&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170714</a><br />\n泛民輸硬"},{"pid":"7643269f40139780bfa712d9fb1f9e19913411c1","tid":326375,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:49:57.000Z","msg":"16個項目涉及高達760億元<br />\n起咩咁把炮?"},{"pid":"e1cbd13d2156861846a78f924d0d0b48c47b3d35","tid":326375,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:51:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>16個項目涉及高達760億元<br />\n起咩咁把炮?</blockquote><br />\n第二條高鐵 (好似係)"},{"pid":"863e580812408fedecdfd49ab9f5321db775015f","tid":326375,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>16個項目涉及高達760億元<br />\n起咩咁把炮?</blockquote><br />\n第二條高鐵 (好似係)</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9637d7419b2e1fe989df02a82e078e1a6b733a0b","tid":326375,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:13:47.000Z","msg":"八婆假到呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}